milestones.description: Haynes's 148 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for WI), surpassing Viv Richards's 119
Gary Cosier and Steve Rixon's 73-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 55 between Doug Walters and Gary Gilmour
Deryck Murray and Haynes's 126-run partnership is WI's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 46 between Clive Lloyd and Julien
